It’s interesting to see Koreans talking about the homelessness in the US. I think a lot of them have this idea in their head of what America is but when they get here and see all the people living in squalor they realize it’s not as pretty as they previously thought. America has a serious homeless issue and it’s only getting worse, it’s a massive stain on our country at the moment as nobody seems to have any solutions to the issue. It’s very sad.
